verses.verse: Jehovah <WH3068> reigneth<WH4427>; He is clothed<WH3847> with majesty<WH1348>; Jehovah<WH3068> is clothed<WH3847> with strength<WH5797>; he hath girded<WH247> himself therewith<WH8398>: The world also is established<WH3559>, that it cannot be moved<WH4131>.
Thy throne<WH3678> is established<WH3559> of old<WH227>: Thou art from everlasting<WH5769>.
The floods<WH5104> have lifted up<WH5375>, O Jehovah<WH3068>, The floods<WH5104> have lifted up<WH5375> their voice<WH6963>; The floods<WH5104> lift up<WH5375> their waves<WH1796>.
Above the voices<WH6963> of many<WH7227> waters<WH4325>, The mighty<WH117> breakers<WH4867> of the sea<WH3220>, Jehovah<WH3068> on high<WH4791> is mighty<WH117>.
Thy testimonies<WH5713> are very<WH3966> sure<WH539>: Holiness<WH6944> becometh<WH4998> thy house<WH1004>, O Jehovah<WH3068>, for evermore<WH753>.
